c0000000
00:01:34.550 --> 00:01:36.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
So that's Auberst,</b></Default>

c0000001
00:01:36.680 --> 00:01:39.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the largest magical city
in the Northern Lands.</b></Default>

c0000002
00:01:39.890 --> 00:01:41.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
We still have a long way to go.</b></Default>

c0000003
00:01:41.850 --> 00:01:44.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's hope we can hitch
a ride on a carriage.</b></Default>

c0000004
00:01:44.310 --> 00:01:46.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000005
00:01:46.270 --> 00:01:47.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, we'll stay there
until you can get your</b></Default>

c0000006
00:01:48.070 --> 00:01:50.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>first-class mage certification,</b></Default>

c0000007
00:01:50.190 --> 00:01:52.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then enter
the Northern Plateau.</b></Default>

c0000008
00:01:52.570 --> 00:01:54.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't think there's
any particular reason</b></Default>

c0000009
00:01:54.450 --> 00:01:56.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have to be the one
to get certified.</b></Default>

c0000010
00:01:56.740 --> 00:01:59.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I won't be able to use it
for long, anyway.</b></Default>

c0000011
00:01:59.620 --> 00:02:01.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
You should take the test, Fern.</b></Default>

c0000012
00:02:01.710 --> 00:02:04.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You really don't know
this stuff, do you?</b></Default>

c0000013
00:02:04.460 --> 00:02:06.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Not just anyone can pass.</b></Default>

c0000014
00:02:06.380 --> 00:02:08.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of all the skilled mages
out there,</b></Default>

c0000015
00:02:08.210 --> 00:02:09.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>only a fraction have
ever reached the rank</b></Default>

c0000016
00:02:10.130 --> 00:02:11.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of first class.</b></Default>

c0000017
00:02:12.260 --> 00:02:14.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I certainly couldn't do it.</b></Default>

c0000018
00:02:14.760 --> 00:02:16.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah.</b></Default>

c0000019
00:02:16.260 --> 00:02:17.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Interesting.</b></Default>

c0000020
00:02:17.600 --> 00:02:20.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You don't sound interested.</b></Default>

c0000021
00:02:20.470 --> 00:02:22.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
I should've asked sooner,</b></Default>

c0000022
00:02:22.430 --> 00:02:23.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but why do we need
to be accompanied</b></Default>

c0000023
00:02:23.850 --> 00:02:27.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by a crazy-powerful mage
to enter the Northern Plateau?</b></Default>

c0000024
00:02:27.360 --> 00:02:29.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] To increase
the chances of survival.</b></Default>

c0000025
00:02:29.610 --> 00:02:31.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That area has long been home
to many cunning,</b></Default>

c0000026
00:02:31.900 --> 00:02:34.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>magic-using monsters
like the Einsam.</b></Default>

c0000027
00:02:34.700 --> 00:02:36.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There was as time
when you wouldn't have dreamed</b></Default>

c0000028
00:02:36.280 --> 00:02:39.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of crossing it without both
a skilled mage and a priest.</b></Default>

c0000029
00:02:40.450 --> 00:02:42.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The travel restrictions
they have in place suggest</b></Default>

c0000030
00:02:42.750 --> 00:02:44.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that danger is on the rise
again in the region.</b></Default>

c0000031
00:02:46.000 --> 00:02:48.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Something fairly serious
must be happening</b></Default>

c0000032
00:02:48.170 --> 00:02:49.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>out on the Plateau.</b></Default>

c0000033
00:02:52.090 --> 00:02:53.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We can find out more
about the exam</b></Default>

c0000034
00:02:53.760 --> 00:02:55.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>once we arrive in the city.</b></Default>

c0000035
00:02:55.550 --> 00:02:58.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But according to Fern,
there will be a combat element.</b></Default>

c0000036
00:02:59.140 --> 00:03:01.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I should contemplate
strategies.</b></Default>

c0000037
00:03:01.890 --> 00:03:03.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Surely you'll be fine, though.</b></Default>

c0000038
00:03:03.730 --> 00:03:06.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>With power like yours,
any test should be a breeze.</b></Default>

c0000039
00:03:06.900 --> 00:03:08.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even when you
are suppressing it,</b></Default>

c0000040
00:03:08.690 --> 00:03:12.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>your mana is still that
of an experienced old mage.</b></Default>

c0000041
00:03:12.280 --> 00:03:14.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll thank you
not to call me an old mage.</b></Default>

c0000042
00:03:14.740 --> 00:03:17.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Aw, and now she's sulking.</b></Default>

c0000043
00:03:17.530 --> 00:03:18.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You couldn't have found
some other way</b></Default>

c0000044
00:03:18.990 --> 00:03:20.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to describe her than that?</b></Default>

c0000045
00:03:20.410 --> 00:03:21.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fine, I apologize.</b></Default>

c0000046
00:03:23.200 --> 00:03:25.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's better than calling me
an old hag,</b></Default>

c0000047
00:03:25.210 --> 00:03:27.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>like someone else once did.</b></Default>

c0000048
00:03:27.080 --> 00:03:28.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
How long ago was that?</b></Default>

c0000049
00:03:29.250 --> 00:03:31.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Forget it, nap time.</b></Default>

c0000050
00:03:31.290 --> 00:03:34.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wake me up
when we get to Auberst.</b></Default>

c0000051
00:03:34.300 --> 00:03:35.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sheesh.</b></Default>

c0000052
00:03:39.010 --> 00:03:40.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Never mind.</b></Default>

c0000053
00:03:40.550 --> 00:03:42.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why?
Is something wrong?</b></Default>

c0000054
00:03:42.640 --> 00:03:45.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] My view of the sky
was partially obscured.</b></Default>

c0000055
00:03:47.230 --> 00:03:48.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
What?</b></Default>

c0000056
00:03:48.480 --> 00:03:52.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just so you know, Fern,
mana is far from the only thing</b></Default>

c0000057
00:03:52.610 --> 00:03:54.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that determines
a mage's strength.</b></Default>

c0000058
00:03:54.820 --> 00:03:56.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Technique and experience,</b></Default>

c0000059
00:03:56.570 --> 00:03:58.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the spells they use,
their control.</b></Default>

c0000060
00:03:58.660 --> 00:04:00.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Never mind tenacity and effort.</b></Default>

c0000061
00:04:00.870 --> 00:04:03.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Some of those sound
more like warrior traits.</b></Default>

c0000062
00:04:03.620 --> 00:04:05.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Finally, there's talent.</b></Default>

c0000063
00:04:06.330 --> 00:04:08.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All of these factors
come into play.</b></Default>

c0000064
00:04:08.750 --> 00:04:11.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In my life, I've lost
eleven times to mages</b></Default>

c0000065
00:04:11.250 --> 00:04:12.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who had less mana than I did.</b></Default>

c0000066
00:04:14.170 --> 00:04:15.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Four of those times
were to demons.</b></Default>

c0000067
00:04:16.720 --> 00:04:19.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Including Qual, years ago.</b></Default>

c0000068
00:04:19.720 --> 00:04:22.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One loss
was to an elf like me,</b></Default>

c0000069
00:04:22.510 --> 00:04:24.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and the remaining six
were to humans.</b></Default>

c0000070
00:04:27.600 --> 00:04:29.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I should have eyes
on the graf's city</b></Default>

c0000071
00:04:29.600 --> 00:04:30.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>before much longer.</b></Default>

c0000072
00:04:32.310 --> 00:04:34.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[UBEL] The road to Auberst
hasn't been an easy one.</b></Default>

c0000073
00:04:35.780 --> 00:04:37.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Guess I'll take a little break.</b></Default>

c0000074
00:04:40.410 --> 00:04:41.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE BANDIT 18A]
That's an awfully nice staff</b></Default>

c0000075
00:04:41.780 --> 00:04:43.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you've got there.</b></Default>

c0000076
00:04:45.700 --> 00:04:47.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, what's this?</b></Default>

c0000077
00:04:47.210 --> 00:04:49.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yet another group
of filthy bandits?</b></Default>

c0000078
00:04:49.830 --> 00:04:51.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[UBEL] You'd think
things would be peaceful</b></Default>

c0000079
00:04:51.290 --> 00:04:52.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>now that Aura's been defeated.</b></Default>

c0000080
00:04:53.710 --> 00:04:56.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Instead, we just get
a different kind of trouble.</b></Default>

c0000081
00:04:56.800 --> 00:05:01.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Save your speeches, lady,
just hand over the goods and...</b></Default>

c0000082
00:05:01.640 --> 00:05:03.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000083
00:05:04.220 --> 00:05:05.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000084
00:05:07.020 --> 00:05:09.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You bastard!</b></Default>

c0000085
00:05:09.600 --> 00:05:10.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000086
00:05:11.650 --> 00:05:12.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000087
00:05:12.940 --> 00:05:14.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000088
00:05:16.440 --> 00:05:19.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you value your lives,
then I suggest you leave.</b></Default>

c0000089
00:05:19.900 --> 00:05:21.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

c0000090
00:05:21.320 --> 00:05:23.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's get out of here.</b></Default>

c0000091
00:05:23.240 --> 00:05:24.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000092
00:05:24.910 --> 00:05:27.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[UBEL]
My hero, thanks for the rescue.</b></Default>

c0000093
00:05:28.620 --> 00:05:30.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm Ubel the Mage, by the way.</b></Default>

c0000094
00:05:31.330 --> 00:05:33.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I'm Kraft the Monk.</b></Default>

c0000095
00:05:33.580 --> 00:05:36.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nice ears,
you must be an elf.</b></Default>

c0000096
00:05:36.090 --> 00:05:38.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've never met
one of your kind before.</b></Default>

c0000097
00:05:40.130 --> 00:05:42.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have the flat eyes
of a killer.</b></Default>

c0000098
00:05:45.600 --> 00:05:47.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Rescuing you
wasn't my goal here.</b></Default>

c0000099
00:05:48.980 --> 00:05:50.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KRAFT] I found
the torn-up bodies of bandits</b></Default>

c0000100
00:05:50.890 --> 00:05:53.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the woods nearby.</b></Default>

c0000101
00:05:53.190 --> 00:05:55.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They'd been killed by a mage.</b></Default>

c0000102
00:05:55.400 --> 00:05:56.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One with tremendous skill.</b></Default>

c0000103
00:05:58.650 --> 00:06:00.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[UBEL]
Ah, I see.</b></Default>

c0000104
00:06:01.740 --> 00:06:03.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So you came
to lecture me, then?</b></Default>

c0000105
00:06:05.240 --> 00:06:08.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No lecture,
I'm just an adventurer.</b></Default>

c0000106
00:06:08.200 --> 00:06:10.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I won't criticize you
for defending yourself,</b></Default>

c0000107
00:06:10.910 --> 00:06:13.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>though the cost was high.</b></Default>

c0000108
00:06:13.120 --> 00:06:15.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KRAFT] I was simply
saving what lives I could.</b></Default>

c0000109
00:06:16.250 --> 00:06:18.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're a shrewd old man,
how boring.</b></Default>

c0000110
00:06:19.630 --> 00:06:22.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KRAFT]
Are you on the road to Auberst?</b></Default>

c0000111
00:06:22.090 --> 00:06:23.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

c0000112
00:06:23.180 --> 00:06:26.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm taking the first class
mage certification exam.</b></Default>

c0000113
00:06:27.310 --> 00:06:29.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Interesting,
that was Frieren's plan, too.</b></Default>

c0000114
00:06:32.310 --> 00:06:34.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KRAFT] She should have
some good stories to share</b></Default>

c0000115
00:06:34.150 --> 00:06:35.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the next time we meet.</b></Default>

c0000116
00:06:37.520 --> 00:06:39.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FEMALE CLERK 18A] The exam
will take place in two months.</b></Default>

c0000117
00:06:39.980 --> 00:06:42.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This will be your last chance
for some time,</b></Default>

c0000118
00:06:42.610 --> 00:06:45.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as it is only administered once
every three years.</b></Default>

c0000119
00:06:46.030 --> 00:06:48.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Also, a fifth-class mage
or higher certification</b></Default>

c0000120
00:06:49.080 --> 00:06:50.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is required to sit the exam.</b></Default>

c0000121
00:06:53.790 --> 00:06:55.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Well, Fern, it's up to you.</b></Default>

c0000122
00:06:57.500 --> 00:07:00.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mistress Frieren,
I can't do this alone.</b></Default>

c0000123
00:07:00.840 --> 00:07:02.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sure you can.</b></Default>

c0000124
00:07:02.420 --> 00:07:04.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And what happens if I fail?</b></Default>

c0000125
00:07:04.470 --> 00:07:07.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are we going to wait
three years for the next exam?</b></Default>

c0000126
00:07:07.180 --> 00:07:09.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll either hire ourselves
a first-class mage,</b></Default>

c0000127
00:07:09.760 --> 00:07:11.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or travel by sea.</b></Default>

c0000128
00:07:11.810 --> 00:07:14.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That would be incredibly
expensive, though.</b></Default>

c0000129
00:07:14.640 --> 00:07:17.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We wouldn't be able
to afford snacks anymore.</b></Default>

c0000130
00:07:20.270 --> 00:07:22.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I don't have
any kind of certification.</b></Default>

c0000131
00:07:23.900 --> 00:07:25.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait...</b></Default>

c0000132
00:07:26.860 --> 00:07:28.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
I do have my holy emblem.</b></Default>

c0000133
00:07:28.990 --> 00:07:30.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Will that work?</b></Default>

c0000134
00:07:31.160 --> 00:07:34.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] I still don't get the
significance of that antique.</b></Default>

c0000135
00:07:34.620 --> 00:07:35.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LERNEN]
Excuse me.</b></Default>

c0000136
00:07:37.210 --> 00:07:39.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Might I take a look
at that pendant, please?</b></Default>

c0000137
00:07:39.920 --> 00:07:41.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000138
00:07:42.340 --> 00:07:43.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000139
00:07:44.840 --> 00:07:45.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[clears throat]</b></Default>

c0000140
00:07:46.010 --> 00:07:49.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Correct me if I'm wrong, but
are you here for the mage exam?</b></Default>

c0000141
00:07:49.760 --> 00:07:50.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both gasp]</b></Default>

c0000142
00:07:52.760 --> 00:07:55.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Looks like I get
to take it after all.</b></Default>

c0000143
00:07:55.180 --> 00:07:56.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm surprised
there's anyone around</b></Default>

c0000144
00:07:56.560 --> 00:07:57.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who still knows what this is.</b></Default>

c0000145
00:07:59.020 --> 00:08:02.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] He acted like
it was something impressive.</b></Default>

c0000146
00:08:02.270 --> 00:08:03.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Well, it's supposed to be.</b></Default>

c0000147
00:08:07.320 --> 00:08:11.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL] Frieren, you're not
part of a magic guild, are you?</b></Default>

c0000148
00:08:11.160 --> 00:08:12.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The organizations
that manage magic</b></Default>

c0000149
00:08:13.040 --> 00:08:15.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are constantly changing.</b></Default>

c0000150
00:08:15.120 --> 00:08:17.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] I can't join a new
one every time they do.</b></Default>

c0000151
00:08:17.910 --> 00:08:19.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

c0000152
00:08:19.920 --> 00:08:22.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Besides,
I have this to identify me.</b></Default>

c0000153
00:08:22.880 --> 00:08:25.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A genuine holy emblem,
impressive, right?</b></Default>

c0000154
00:08:27.340 --> 00:08:29.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have no clue
what this rusty thing is.</b></Default>

c0000155
00:08:29.970 --> 00:08:31.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Heiter?
-None at all.</b></Default>

c0000156
00:08:35.100 --> 00:08:36.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000157
00:08:38.230 --> 00:08:39.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fine.</b></Default>

c0000158
00:08:40.270 --> 00:08:42.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] But this is the only
thing that proves I'm a mage,</b></Default>

c0000159
00:08:42.860 --> 00:08:44.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so if you don't recognize it...</b></Default>

c0000160
00:08:45.070 --> 00:08:46.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[smiles]</b></Default>

c0000161
00:08:46.740 --> 00:08:49.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL] Frieren, we may not
understand the significance</b></Default>

c0000162
00:08:49.650 --> 00:08:51.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of that necklace.</b></Default>

c0000163
00:08:51.410 --> 00:08:53.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But still, we know
what you're capable of,</b></Default>

c0000164
00:08:53.910 --> 00:08:56.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and we know that
you're an incredible mage.</b></Default>

c0000165
00:08:56.870 --> 00:08:58.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Isn't that enough?</b></Default>

c0000166
00:09:00.500 --> 00:09:02.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
You'll die so soon, though.</b></Default>

c0000167
00:09:03.460 --> 00:09:04.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[smiles]</b></Default>

c0000168
00:09:05.040 --> 00:09:06.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000169
00:09:09.180 --> 00:09:10.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Mistress Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000170
00:09:11.840 --> 00:09:14.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We may not know
what that thing is,</b></Default>

c0000171
00:09:14.180 --> 00:09:16.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but we do know that
you're an incredible mage.</b></Default>

c0000172
00:09:22.310 --> 00:09:23.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Good point, Fern.</b></Default>

c0000173
00:09:24.980 --> 00:09:26.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

c0000174
00:09:26.900 --> 00:09:30.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] According to the
Continental Magic Association,</b></Default>

c0000175
00:09:30.320 --> 00:09:31.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a person becomes a proper mage</b></Default>

c0000176
00:09:32.030 --> 00:09:34.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>once they have achieved
at least a fifth-class ranking.</b></Default>

c0000177
00:09:35.530 --> 00:09:38.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why did you get
a third-class certification?</b></Default>

c0000178
00:09:38.620 --> 00:09:41.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was the one with the
soonest available testing date.</b></Default>

c0000179
00:09:42.870 --> 00:09:44.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Apparently, there are 600 mages</b></Default>

c0000180
00:09:44.830 --> 00:09:46.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who are at least fifth-class.</b></Default>

c0000181
00:09:46.920 --> 00:09:49.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you include apprentices
from sixth to ninth class,</b></Default>

c0000182
00:09:49.550 --> 00:09:51.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there are 2,000 mages total.</b></Default>

c0000183
00:09:52.130 --> 00:09:54.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Among them, 45 are first-class.</b></Default>

c0000184
00:09:54.550 --> 00:09:57.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That exam is held
every three years.</b></Default>

c0000185
00:09:57.220 --> 00:09:59.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here, at the northern branch
in Auberst</b></Default>

c0000186
00:09:59.310 --> 00:10:01.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and at the headquarters
in the holy city of Strahl.</b></Default>

c0000187
00:10:03.690 --> 00:10:06.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Many years, no one
passes the test at all.</b></Default>

c0000188
00:10:06.400 --> 00:10:08.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Injury and death
are expected outcomes.</b></Default>

c0000189
00:10:09.860 --> 00:10:11.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sounds moderately challenging.</b></Default>

c0000190
00:10:12.860 --> 00:10:16.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Either way, there are a lot
fewer mages around these days.</b></Default>

c0000191
00:10:16.530 --> 00:10:18.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
There used to be more of us?</b></Default>

c0000192
00:10:19.200 --> 00:10:20.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] A century ago,
when the Demon King's</b></Default>

c0000193
00:10:21.040 --> 00:10:23.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>attacks intensified,
you would almost certainly</b></Default>

c0000194
00:10:23.620 --> 00:10:24.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>encounter at least one mage</b></Default>

c0000195
00:10:25.040 --> 00:10:27.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>while strolling through
any given town.</b></Default>

c0000196
00:10:27.290 --> 00:10:30.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>These days, you hardly see them
outside of the magic cities.</b></Default>

c0000197
00:10:30.760 --> 00:10:32.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh.</b></Default>

c0000198
00:10:32.300 --> 00:10:34.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] There are
two months until the exam.</b></Default>

c0000199
00:10:34.680 --> 00:10:36.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We should spend them training.</b></Default>

c0000200
00:10:37.260 --> 00:10:39.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000201
00:11:08.840 --> 00:11:10.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GENAU]
Attention, please.</b></Default>

c0000202
00:11:10.380 --> 00:11:13.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The first-class mage exam
will begin momentarily.</b></Default>

c0000203
00:11:14.510 --> 00:11:16.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This year's test-takers
seem rather exceptional.</b></Default>

c0000204
00:11:17.840 --> 00:11:19.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FALSCH] There's Wirbel,
a second-class mage</b></Default>

c0000205
00:11:19.930 --> 00:11:22.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and the captain
of the Northern Magic Corps.</b></Default>

c0000206
00:11:22.270 --> 00:11:23.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's fought against
the remnants</b></Default>

c0000207
00:11:23.520 --> 00:11:25.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the Demon King's forces
for years now.</b></Default>

c0000208
00:11:26.730 --> 00:11:28.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That crafty looking
older gentleman passed</b></Default>

c0000209
00:11:28.690 --> 00:11:31.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the second-class exam
with flying colors.</b></Default>

c0000210
00:11:31.280 --> 00:11:33.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He became an imperial mage
after surviving</b></Default>

c0000211
00:11:33.240 --> 00:11:34.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a bloody power struggle.</b></Default>

c0000212
00:11:34.900 --> 00:11:36.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Denken will be one to watch.</b></Default>

c0000213
00:11:37.070 --> 00:11:39.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And then we have Fern,
the youngest mage</b></Default>

c0000214
00:11:39.620 --> 00:11:41.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to ever receive
a third-class certification</b></Default>

c0000215
00:11:41.410 --> 00:11:42.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with top marks.</b></Default>

c0000216
00:11:42.660 --> 00:11:44.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Undoubtedly a good egg.</b></Default>

c0000217
00:11:44.700 --> 00:11:46.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But we have bad eggs, too.</b></Default>

c0000218
00:11:47.790 --> 00:11:49.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That girl is Ubel.</b></Default>

c0000219
00:11:49.540 --> 00:11:51.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's a third-class mage
who was disqualified</b></Default>

c0000220
00:11:51.790 --> 00:11:54.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from the second-class exam
two years ago,</b></Default>

c0000221
00:11:54.260 --> 00:11:57.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when she killed the first-class
mage who proctored it.</b></Default>

c0000222
00:11:57.260 --> 00:11:58.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My.</b></Default>

c0000223
00:11:58.470 --> 00:12:00.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>See any other promising faces?</b></Default>

c0000224
00:12:01.100 --> 00:12:02.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000225
00:12:02.720 --> 00:12:04.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FALSCH] That woman
is radiating the mana</b></Default>

c0000226
00:12:04.640 --> 00:12:06.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of an experienced old mage.</b></Default>

c0000227
00:12:08.270 --> 00:12:10.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Know her?
-I don't.</b></Default>

c0000228
00:12:11.020 --> 00:12:12.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Listen closely.</b></Default>

c0000229
00:12:12.570 --> 00:12:15.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I will now announce the
content of your first trial.</b></Default>

c0000230
00:12:15.820 --> 00:12:19.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GENAU] You will not be tested
on your own, but as a party.</b></Default>

c0000231
00:12:19.200 --> 00:12:21.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The 57 exam-takers
will be split up</b></Default>

c0000232
00:12:21.660 --> 00:12:22.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>into groups of three.</b></Default>

c0000233
00:12:24.160 --> 00:12:25.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We will now assign
your parties.</b></Default>

c0000234
00:12:28.830 --> 00:12:30.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Interesting.</b></Default>

c0000235
00:12:30.540 --> 00:12:33.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're engraved with numbers.</b></Default>

c0000236
00:12:33.090 --> 00:12:34.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Seems I'm in the second
party, then.</b></Default>

c0000237
00:12:36.970 --> 00:12:38.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Imbuing the bracelets
with mana allows us</b></Default>

c0000238
00:12:39.010 --> 00:12:41.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to quickly locate
our teammates.</b></Default>

c0000239
00:12:41.260 --> 00:12:44.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A unique alternative
to reading off names.</b></Default>

c0000240
00:12:44.390 --> 00:12:46.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This should be amusing,
to say the least.</b></Default>

c0000241
00:12:47.520 --> 00:12:50.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>These party compositions
are far from normal.</b></Default>

c0000242
00:12:50.730 --> 00:12:53.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're bound to end up
with groups of magical misfits</b></Default>

c0000243
00:12:53.360 --> 00:12:54.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that can't work together</b></Default>

c0000244
00:12:55.070 --> 00:12:56.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and struggle
to relinquish control.</b></Default>

c0000245
00:12:57.900 --> 00:13:00.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>First impressions
are important, here.</b></Default>

c0000246
00:13:00.740 --> 00:13:02.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I should be careful
not to make any waves.</b></Default>

c0000247
00:13:04.280 --> 00:13:06.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I sense my teammates'
bracelets nearby.</b></Default>

c0000248
00:13:07.040 --> 00:13:08.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KANNE]
Okay, that's enough, already!</b></Default>

c0000249
00:13:08.580 --> 00:13:09.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ow, ow, ow!</b></Default>

c0000250
00:13:09.790 --> 00:13:11.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're gonna rip them
off my head, you jerk!</b></Default>

c0000251
00:13:12.040 --> 00:13:13.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm gonna kill you,
you hear me?</b></Default>

c0000252
00:13:13.420 --> 00:13:15.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-I dare you.
-Ow! Get off!</b></Default>

c0000253
00:13:16.880 --> 00:13:18.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Violence has been chosen.</b></Default>

c0000254
00:13:23.800 --> 00:13:25.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nice to meet ya.</b></Default>

c0000255
00:13:26.140 --> 00:13:27.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's nice to meet you, too.</b></Default>

c0000256
00:13:29.770 --> 00:13:30.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

c0000257
00:13:31.060 --> 00:13:32.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now that we've reached
the testing area,</b></Default>

c0000258
00:13:32.940 --> 00:13:34.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I will explain
your instructions.</b></Default>

c0000259
00:13:36.230 --> 00:13:38.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GENAU] This place is home
to a small species of bird</b></Default>

c0000260
00:13:38.650 --> 00:13:39.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>known as the Stille.</b></Default>

c0000261
00:13:41.070 --> 00:13:44.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As you can see, each party
has been given one cage.</b></Default>

c0000262
00:13:44.370 --> 00:13:45.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There are two conditions
you must fulfill</b></Default>

c0000263
00:13:46.030 --> 00:13:47.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to pass this initial test.</b></Default>

c0000264
00:13:48.200 --> 00:13:50.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The first of which
is by sunset tomorrow,</b></Default>

c0000265
00:13:50.160 --> 00:13:51.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>your cage
must contain a Stille.</b></Default>

c0000266
00:13:52.830 --> 00:13:54.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[KANNE] Get away from me!
-[GENAU] The second requirement</b></Default>

c0000267
00:13:54.630 --> 00:13:55.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is that all party members</b></Default>

c0000268
00:13:55.790 --> 00:13:58.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are present at that time.</b></Default>

c0000269
00:13:58.170 --> 00:14:00.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For the most part,
you are free to do as you wish,</b></Default>

c0000270
00:14:00.880 --> 00:14:04.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but if anyone is foolish enough
to leave the testing area,</b></Default>

c0000271
00:14:04.600 --> 00:14:07.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they and their entire party
will be failed immediately.</b></Default>

c0000272
00:14:08.720 --> 00:14:11.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That shouldn't be a problem,
considering there's a barrier</b></Default>

c0000273
00:14:11.180 --> 00:14:12.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>around the testing site
that not so much</b></Default>

c0000274
00:14:12.940 --> 00:14:14.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as a speck of dust
could get through.</b></Default>

c0000275
00:14:15.020 --> 00:14:17.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're stuck,
whether we wanna be or not.</b></Default>

c0000276
00:14:17.480 --> 00:14:19.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You two were listening
through your combat.</b></Default>

c0000277
00:14:20.400 --> 00:14:23.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GENAU] Ready yourselves,
the first test begins now.</b></Default>

c0000278
00:14:23.610 --> 00:14:25.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Before we do anything,
we need to come up with</b></Default>

c0000279
00:14:25.410 --> 00:14:27.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-a solid plan!
-How stupid are you?</b></Default>

c0000280
00:14:27.740 --> 00:14:29.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A plan won't do us any good
if we can't find a bird</b></Default>

c0000281
00:14:29.790 --> 00:14:32.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-in the first place!
-Violence is the default.</b></Default>

c0000282
00:14:33.000 --> 00:14:34.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

c0000283
00:14:34.290 --> 00:14:36.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why don't we get moving,
and introduce ourselves</b></Default>

c0000284
00:14:36.460 --> 00:14:37.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>while we're at it?</b></Default>

c0000285
00:14:37.500 --> 00:14:38.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

c0000286
00:14:40.380 --> 00:14:41.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Also?</b></Default>

c0000287
00:14:41.470 --> 00:14:43.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Use rock-paper-scissors
to decide</b></Default>

c0000288
00:14:43.260 --> 00:14:44.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who will carry the cage.</b></Default>

c0000289
00:14:44.470 --> 00:14:45.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000290
00:14:50.310 --> 00:14:52.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can call me Frieren.
And you are?</b></Default>

c0000291
00:14:53.350 --> 00:14:56.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lawine,
I am a third-class mage.</b></Default>

c0000292
00:14:56.610 --> 00:14:59.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm Kanne, I'm a third-class
mage like she is.</b></Default>

c0000293
00:14:59.820 --> 00:15:01.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The two of us go way back.</b></Default>

c0000294
00:15:01.570 --> 00:15:03.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We graduated
from the same magic school.</b></Default>

c0000295
00:15:04.610 --> 00:15:06.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Did they happen
to teach you anything</b></Default>

c0000296
00:15:06.360 --> 00:15:07.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about the Stille there?</b></Default>

c0000297
00:15:07.700 --> 00:15:09.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[LAWINE] No.
-[KANNE] Nuh-uh.</b></Default>

c0000298
00:15:09.490 --> 00:15:11.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have a fair bit
of knowledge on them,</b></Default>

c0000299
00:15:11.700 --> 00:15:14.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I've never seen one
in person before.</b></Default>

c0000300
00:15:14.250 --> 00:15:16.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's start by finding
a Stille and observing it.</b></Default>

c0000301
00:15:17.750 --> 00:15:19.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000302
00:15:38.400 --> 00:15:39.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KANNE]
I'm exhausted.</b></Default>

c0000303
00:15:40.820 --> 00:15:42.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You are so undisciplined.</b></Default>

c0000304
00:15:42.650 --> 00:15:44.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think we could all
use a break.</b></Default>

c0000305
00:15:47.780 --> 00:15:50.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Since I feel all right,
I'll check things out up ahead.</b></Default>

c0000306
00:15:50.410 --> 00:15:53.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's way safer for everyone
if we stay together.</b></Default>

c0000307
00:15:53.370 --> 00:15:56.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, great idea, if you want
to waste all our time.</b></Default>

c0000308
00:15:57.460 --> 00:15:59.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lawine, are you strong?</b></Default>

c0000309
00:15:59.420 --> 00:16:00.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Stronger than her.</b></Default>

c0000310
00:16:00.880 --> 00:16:02.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You wanna fight, huh?</b></Default>

c0000311
00:16:02.880 --> 00:16:04.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you stronger than me?</b></Default>

c0000312
00:16:04.630 --> 00:16:05.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

c0000313
00:16:06.010 --> 00:16:07.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE] I wouldn't
want to fight you, no.</b></Default>

c0000314
00:16:09.300 --> 00:16:11.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
I see, fine.</b></Default>

c0000315
00:16:11.260 --> 00:16:12.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Go on, then.</b></Default>

c0000316
00:16:12.760 --> 00:16:15.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come back if it starts
looking too dangerous.</b></Default>

c0000317
00:16:15.470 --> 00:16:16.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right.</b></Default>

c0000318
00:16:16.890 --> 00:16:19.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And make sure
that you watch the skies.</b></Default>

c0000319
00:16:19.190 --> 00:16:20.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Way ahead of you.</b></Default>

c0000320
00:16:22.360 --> 00:16:23.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000321
00:16:23.900 --> 00:16:26.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] I fear
the worst for this party.</b></Default>

c0000322
00:16:26.820 --> 00:16:29.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wow, Frieren,
you're kinda like our teacher.</b></Default>

c0000323
00:16:29.820 --> 00:16:31.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And you're a super good
leader, too.</b></Default>

c0000324
00:16:31.740 --> 00:16:34.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your constant fighting
has thrust me into the role.</b></Default>

c0000325
00:16:34.540 --> 00:16:36.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd rather not be in charge.</b></Default>

c0000326
00:16:36.500 --> 00:16:37.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I'm sorry.</b></Default>

c0000327
00:16:37.830 --> 00:16:40.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For whatever reason, we've
kinda always been like this.</b></Default>

c0000328
00:16:41.540 --> 00:16:43.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But real quick,
what did you mean by that?</b></Default>

c0000329
00:16:43.710 --> 00:16:46.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Why watch the skies?
-I meant exactly what I said.</b></Default>

c0000330
00:16:47.800 --> 00:16:49.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you detect mana well?</b></Default>

c0000331
00:16:50.470 --> 00:16:51.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, why?</b></Default>

c0000332
00:16:51.970 --> 00:16:53.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE]
Hey.</b></Default>

c0000333
00:16:53.970 --> 00:16:55.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
That was quick.</b></Default>

c0000334
00:16:55.100 --> 00:16:56.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I came across a Stille.</b></Default>

c0000335
00:16:59.980 --> 00:17:01.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Nicely done, Lawine.</b></Default>

c0000336
00:17:01.650 --> 00:17:03.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now watch it closely.</b></Default>

c0000337
00:17:04.480 --> 00:17:06.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000338
00:17:08.900 --> 00:17:11.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I told you to watch it,
not catch it.</b></Default>

c0000339
00:17:11.410 --> 00:17:12.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's going to fly away.</b></Default>

c0000340
00:17:12.620 --> 00:17:14.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE]
I think not.</b></Default>

c0000341
00:17:14.200 --> 00:17:15.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's pretty nice work, Kanne.</b></Default>

c0000342
00:17:20.210 --> 00:17:21.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah, not bad.</b></Default>

c0000343
00:17:24.460 --> 00:17:26.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you really should get down
before it's too late.</b></Default>

c0000344
00:17:26.880 --> 00:17:28.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?
What for?</b></Default>

c0000345
00:17:29.680 --> 00:17:30.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000346
00:17:30.930 --> 00:17:32.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[grunting]
-[water splashing]</b></Default>

c0000347
00:17:34.100 --> 00:17:36.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Stille are incredible
little creatures.</b></Default>

c0000348
00:17:36.350 --> 00:17:39.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At top speed, they move
faster than sound itself.</b></Default>

c0000349
00:17:39.430 --> 00:17:41.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Trying to restrain
one like that is pointless.</b></Default>

c0000350
00:17:43.150 --> 00:17:45.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE] It was right there,
we almost had it.</b></Default>

c0000351
00:17:45.270 --> 00:17:46.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KANNE]
We were so close.</b></Default>

c0000352
00:17:46.780 --> 00:17:49.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Capturing one is going
to require careful observation.</b></Default>

c0000353
00:17:50.070 --> 00:17:51.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll use the remainder
of the day</b></Default>

c0000354
00:17:51.400 --> 00:17:52.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to learn more
about their behavior.</b></Default>

c0000355
00:17:54.530 --> 00:17:57.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Kanne used her magic
to control the water</b></Default>

c0000356
00:17:57.240 --> 00:17:59.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and Lawine used hers
to freeze it.</b></Default>

c0000357
00:17:59.620 --> 00:18:02.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Their timing
was perfectly coordinated.</b></Default>

c0000358
00:18:02.290 --> 00:18:04.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Superb teamwork indeed.</b></Default>

c0000359
00:18:04.580 --> 00:18:07.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You couldn't achieve
something like that overnight.</b></Default>

c0000360
00:18:07.710 --> 00:18:09.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was worried
for a while there,</b></Default>

c0000361
00:18:09.880 --> 00:18:11.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but this might actually work.</b></Default>

c0000362
00:18:11.590 --> 00:18:12.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's go find it.</b></Default>

c0000363
00:18:14.680 --> 00:18:16.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They must like the lake,
we should stay here!</b></Default>

c0000364
00:18:16.680 --> 00:18:18.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE] If we waste time
on your assumptions,</b></Default>

c0000365
00:18:18.180 --> 00:18:19.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-we'll lose it!
-[FRIEREN] Or maybe not.</b></Default>

c0000366
00:18:19.810 --> 00:18:21.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The violence prevails.</b></Default>

c0000367
00:18:22.390 --> 00:18:23.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000368
00:18:45.040 --> 00:18:46.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[rain splattering]</b></Default>

c0000369
00:18:48.710 --> 00:18:50.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000370
00:18:50.760 --> 00:18:52.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you guys hear that sound?</b></Default>

c0000371
00:18:52.630 --> 00:18:53.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000372
00:18:56.050 --> 00:18:57.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KANNE]
Where'd Frieren go?</b></Default>

c0000373
00:19:01.930 --> 00:19:03.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can barely hear it,</b></Default>

c0000374
00:19:03.310 --> 00:19:04.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but it sounds like rain,
all right.</b></Default>

c0000375
00:19:11.900 --> 00:19:13.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's clearly not raining, so?</b></Default>

c0000376
00:19:14.910 --> 00:19:16.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, I see.</b></Default>

c0000377
00:19:17.450 --> 00:19:18.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This must mean
that we're close to the...</b></Default>

c0000378
00:19:18.830 --> 00:19:19.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000379
00:19:21.410 --> 00:19:23.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000380
00:19:23.750 --> 00:19:25.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A monster!</b></Default>

c0000381
00:19:26.420 --> 00:19:27.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000382
00:19:33.630 --> 00:19:34.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My staff.</b></Default>

c0000383
00:19:37.800 --> 00:19:40.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>La... Lawine!</b></Default>

c0000384
00:19:40.180 --> 00:19:41.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000385
00:19:43.470 --> 00:19:45.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

c0000386
00:19:46.140 --> 00:19:47.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

c0000387
00:19:51.570 --> 00:19:54.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That would be why I told you
to watch the skies.</b></Default>

c0000388
00:19:54.610 --> 00:19:56.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh... Right.</b></Default>

c0000389
00:20:04.450 --> 00:20:06.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Feeling calmer?</b></Default>

c0000390
00:20:06.210 --> 00:20:07.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000391
00:20:08.370 --> 00:20:11.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You called
Lawine's name just then.</b></Default>

c0000392
00:20:11.090 --> 00:20:12.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

c0000393
00:20:13.170 --> 00:20:14.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you don't like Lawine,
do you?</b></Default>

c0000394
00:20:16.380 --> 00:20:17.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, I don't.</b></Default>

c0000395
00:20:18.380 --> 00:20:19.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Clearly.</b></Default>

c0000396
00:20:19.930 --> 00:20:21.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, explain to me
how the two of you</b></Default>

c0000397
00:20:21.720 --> 00:20:23.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>work so well together.</b></Default>

c0000398
00:20:23.680 --> 00:20:24.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
I'm curious.</b></Default>

c0000399
00:20:26.480 --> 00:20:28.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>From time to time,
I can be a coward.</b></Default>

c0000400
00:20:29.980 --> 00:20:31.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In the past,
whenever a critical moment</b></Default>

c0000401
00:20:31.820 --> 00:20:33.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>has popped up,
I completely freeze.</b></Default>

c0000402
00:20:36.740 --> 00:20:38.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KANNE]
It happened the very first time</b></Default>

c0000403
00:20:38.240 --> 00:20:39.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that I had to cast
a flying spell.</b></Default>

c0000404
00:20:40.700 --> 00:20:41.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000405
00:20:43.120 --> 00:20:44.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks to someone's
nail biting,</b></Default>

c0000406
00:20:44.870 --> 00:20:46.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the others are way ahead of us.</b></Default>

c0000407
00:20:46.580 --> 00:20:47.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You'll have
the water beneath you,</b></Default>

c0000408
00:20:47.910 --> 00:20:49.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so it's not like you'll die.</b></Default>

c0000409
00:20:50.710 --> 00:20:53.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you don't have the courage
to do it, I could kick you.</b></Default>

c0000410
00:20:54.130 --> 00:20:55.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I hate your guts, Lawine.</b></Default>

c0000411
00:20:56.630 --> 00:20:58.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE]
I'm well aware.</b></Default>

c0000412
00:20:58.630 --> 00:21:00.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KANNE] I would be braver
if you weren't always</b></Default>

c0000413
00:21:00.380 --> 00:21:01.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so mean to me.</b></Default>

c0000414
00:21:01.800 --> 00:21:03.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm the kind of person
who needs praise</b></Default>

c0000415
00:21:03.760 --> 00:21:05.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to blossom, you know.</b></Default>

c0000416
00:21:06.020 --> 00:21:07.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You must be kidding.</b></Default>

c0000417
00:21:07.680 --> 00:21:09.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is a prime example
of why parents</b></Default>

c0000418
00:21:09.810 --> 00:21:12.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>shouldn't baby their kids
like little princesses.</b></Default>

c0000419
00:21:12.690 --> 00:21:14.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE]
But if it'll help you fly,</b></Default>

c0000420
00:21:14.520 --> 00:21:16.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be as nice as you want.</b></Default>

c0000421
00:21:17.240 --> 00:21:18.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then tell me my strengths.</b></Default>

c0000422
00:21:19.860 --> 00:21:22.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you wanted to kill me,
you should've done it by now.</b></Default>

c0000423
00:21:24.370 --> 00:21:25.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

c0000424
00:21:27.790 --> 00:21:29.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE] Even though
you're a complete coward,</b></Default>

c0000425
00:21:29.790 --> 00:21:31.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you try really hard.</b></Default>

c0000426
00:21:31.540 --> 00:21:32.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000427
00:21:33.920 --> 00:21:35.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You wanted
to hear your strength.</b></Default>

c0000428
00:21:36.380 --> 00:21:39.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, but...tell me some more.</b></Default>

c0000429
00:21:39.380 --> 00:21:40.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What? Seriously?</b></Default>

c0000430
00:21:41.800 --> 00:21:42.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000431
00:21:43.890 --> 00:21:46.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE] You work hard
even when no one's watching,</b></Default>

c0000432
00:21:46.600 --> 00:21:48.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and you're always
very considerate</b></Default>

c0000433
00:21:48.680 --> 00:21:50.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the world around you.</b></Default>

c0000434
00:21:50.980 --> 00:21:52.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>More, please.</b></Default>

c0000435
00:21:52.770 --> 00:21:54.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

c0000436
00:21:55.440 --> 00:21:57.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE] I guess that
you're cute when you smile.</b></Default>

c0000437
00:21:59.030 --> 00:22:01.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KANNE]
Huh? Gross.</b></Default>

c0000438
00:22:01.110 --> 00:22:03.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[screams]</b></Default>

c0000439
00:22:06.620 --> 00:22:08.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yikes, close call.</b></Default>

c0000440
00:22:08.330 --> 00:22:09.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I told you, see?</b></Default>

c0000441
00:22:09.790 --> 00:22:11.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That wasn't so terrifying,
was it?</b></Default>

c0000442
00:22:11.870 --> 00:22:14.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now that you can fly,
I'm done being nice.</b></Default>

c0000443
00:22:15.380 --> 00:22:17.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lawine's rough
around the edges,</b></Default>

c0000444
00:22:17.500 --> 00:22:19.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but she somehow
always pulls me along.</b></Default>

c0000445
00:22:20.340 --> 00:22:22.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She taught me I can do
most anything if I go for it,</b></Default>

c0000446
00:22:23.050 --> 00:22:25.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>no matter how scared
I might feel inside.</b></Default>

c0000447
00:22:27.060 --> 00:22:28.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[smiles]</b></Default>

c0000448
00:22:29.020 --> 00:22:30.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KANNE]
Before you go, Frieren...</b></Default>

c0000449
00:22:33.060 --> 00:22:35.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Listen...I noticed something
that might be handy.</b></Default>

c0000450
00:22:40.900 --> 00:22:42.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you think
it could be useful?</b></Default>

c0000451
00:22:44.240 --> 00:22:46.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, I do, excellent find.</b></Default>

c0000452
00:22:46.740 --> 00:22:48.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We might be able to capture
a Stille, after all.</b></Default>

c0000453
00:24:20.460 --> 00:24:21.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAUFEN]
There's something wrong.</b></Default>

c0000454
00:24:21.460 --> 00:24:22.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE] Fine, let's do this.</b></Default>

c0000455
00:24:22.880 --> 00:24:24.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER]They're all amateurs.
[FRIEREN]Someone's detected us.</b></Default>

c0000456
00:24:24.170 --> 00:24:25.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[UBEL] It's time to spill a
little blood. -[KANNE] Shut up.</b></Default>

c0000457
00:24:25.920 --> 00:24:29.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] This is the second
party's well-laid plan.</b></Default>

